0.37.0

This release re activate kubemacpool using version v0.13.0 to do so some adjustment
have being needed at e2e since looks like there is a race at kubemacpool between
Secret and pod startup.


Features:
* Bump kubemacpool v0.13.0 (#397)

Bugs:
* Ensure components objects deletion and creation at e2e tests (#393)
* Cover all use cases at caBundle (#390)
* keep the order of webhooks while merging (#389)
* status_manager: only require single ready pod for deployment (#388)
* Preserve webhook configuration caBundle and TLS secrets at reconcile (#382)

Infra:
* Add github issue/PR templates (#396)
* Use correct github path for github-release (#379)
